Job Description:
- Gather, analyze, and document business requirements from stakeholders across departments including trading, risk, compliance, and customer service/marketing;
- Collaborate with product managers and development teams to define product features, prioritize backlog items, and ensure alignment with business goals;
- Conduct market and competitor analysis to identify opportunities for new products or enhancements to existing securities products;
- ⁠Monitor product performance and user feedback to recommend continuous improvements and enhancements;
- ⁠Liaise with compliance and legal teams to ensure products meet regulatory requirements.
Requirement :
- Bachelor's Degree in any major, preferably in Computer Science/Engineering/Finance/Economics;
- Less than 3 years of experience as a Business Analyst, Product Analyst, or similar role, preferably in financial services or securities industry;
- Excellent communication, problem-solving, and stakeholder management skills;
- Ability to work collaboratively with multiple functions, including engineering, operations, marketing, and compliance teams.

Job Descriptions
• Gathering information about Customer;
• Determine credit worthiness of Customer;
• Assessing, analyzing and interpreting complicated financial information;
• Making recommendations about procedural/policy changes;
• Prevent, Detect, and Investigation related to Fraudulent Action.
Reqruitments
• Maximum 28 years old;
• Candidate must possess at least Diploma, Bachelor's Degree in any field;
• Required language(s): Bahasa Indonesia, English;
• At least 2 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position, prefer has experience in P2P Lending Money Company;
• Required Skill(s): Good Communication skill, Ability to solve problem, responsible and compressive, able to operate computer and Ms. Office, Indonesia proficient;
• Preferably Staff (non-management & non-supervisor) specialized in Quality Control/Assurance or equivalent;
• Can be flexible with schedule availability and willing to work in shifting;
• Able to operate Computer and Ms. Office (Word, Excel and Power Point);

Full requirment :
a) Memiliki keterampilan dalam analisis, leadership, business process and
planning, serta technical knowledge;
b) Memiliki pengalaman dalam melakukan analisis proses bisnis dan project
management;
c) Menguasai tools project management (Jira, Trello) dan keahlian membuat
report atau laporan project;
d) Memiliki keterampilan SQL minimal basic serta kemampuan design mockup
sistem aplikasi;
e) Memiliki kemampuan data analytic dan system analyst;

Job Description
Examine and evaluate current systems;
Identify system requirements;
Document interfaces and technical;
Lead and guide the team to provide solutions in the application;
Collaborate with internal teams to produce and deliver the best solution;
Comprehensive testing programs;
Train users on the new applications and provide support;
Conduct comparisons between vendors (cost and benefit analysis)
Minimum Qualifications
Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science / Information System / Computerized Accounting with GPA > 3,00;
Mastering the basics of SQL Statement;
Understand database design concepts and techniques and be able to create documentation in the form of ERD;
Understand the forms of transactions and application Reports and can make prototyping transactions and reports using MS Excel;
Have the ability to make application design documentation;
Excellent analytical skills;
A good problem-solving attitude
